title: ytcracker - serious business ep
description:
search itunes or amazon if you feel like spending 6 bucks to "buy" this.

love you all!

dear sir/madam,

i&#039;m all fucked up and i&#039;m uploading this i don&#039;t even know if it is fully mastered but i listened to it and it sounded ok so screw it

anyway this is serious business the six track ep that keeps itunes from deleting me as irrelevant

everyone who has heard it including my brother says it&#039;s pretty awesome and he&#039;s one of my worst critics because he&#039;s a jock and hates nerds but i love him very much

first things first i&#039;d like to dedicate this album to my grandpapa who passed away last july and he always told me to do it my way and so i do and it hasn&#039;t failed me so far

also rip sean you&#039;re forever in my heart as the nerd who left this world too soon thanks for watching over my heart and remember legends never die

this album wouldn&#039;t be possible without elijah lucian who i met through the youtubes and he produced some banging tracks on this ep but i&#039;m sure you can plainly hear that give the man props:

hopefully disney doesn&#039;t sue me for i am a pirate because i didn&#039;t clear the sample i wanted to keep it real like a pirate would oh well it will be good publicity just ask lil flip

the track production is as follows:

hardly tell - elijah lucian

i am a pirate - entity

i did it my way - elijah lucian

i hate my life - da cypha

lay down - elijah lucian

over and over - elijah lucian

i can&#039;t spit individual thanks because i am going to leave someone out and piss them off so stc and dg i love you keep being awesome

by the time this album hits itunes i&#039;ll probably be plastered all over g4 and the 8 bit boys and sinister six projects (lol free music) will be done so google that work and download it because i like giving music away for free i don&#039;t know why i&#039;m even selling music and i don&#039;t care when you pirate it thanks for giving me and my producers money though we DO appreciate it your support is everything to us but mainly keep listening that&#039;s all i ask also read my run on sentences

feel free to hit me up any time - i try to answer ALL fan mail because mister rogers did it and he&#039;s one of my idols and if he can do it anyone can he was mister rogers you and i are not mister rogers he was bigger than the president

regards,

ytcracker
